Usage: setPtnPinStatus [-help] [-selectedPinStatus {fixed placed cover}] { -pin {pinName | pinNameList} } { -status {fixed placed unplaced cover} } { [-pin {pinName | pinNameList} -status {fixed placed unplaced cover} [-cell <partitionName>]] }

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
-cell <partitionName>                     # Specifies name of the partition,
                                          # wildcard can be specified
                                          # (string, optional)
-pin {pinName | pinNameList}              # Specifies name of the partition
                                          # pins, wildcard can be specified
                                          # (string, optional)
-selectedPinStatus {fixed placed cover}   # Select pin with only specified
                                          # status (enum, optional)
-status {fixed placed unplaced cover}     # Specifies new status of the pin
                                          # (enum, optional)